title: Jungle Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Thai, Western, Beer/Wine, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers a very large mainly British style food menu. Makes their own veggie burgers and veggie sausages and have an extensive vegetarian menu. The owners are good at catering to the needs vegetarians and vegans. Has Wi-Fi and big flat screen for sporting events.
